e bright side in the same PSF. We should choose reference\npixels from the same PSF when reducing the dgvAPP360 dataset or the gvAPP180\ndataset with TRAP. In these datasets, TRAP achieves results consistent with\nprevious best detections, with an improved S/N for the gvAPP180 dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 09:52:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
