 string appears as a domain wall\ninside the mother wall triggering the third SSB, which leads to a granddaughter\nmonopole as a kink inside the daughter vortex. We demonstrate numerical\nsimulations for the dynamical evolution of the composite solitons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 12:39:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
